            <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Listen as Étienne’s counselor talks to him about his future. When you hear the counselor use the expressions &lt;i&gt;&lt;strong&gt;quand, lorsque, dès que&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/i&gt; or &lt;strong&gt;&lt;i&gt;aussitôt que&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, write it down along with the verb form in the &lt;strong&gt;&lt;i&gt;futur simple&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, following the model. Copy and paste these special characters whenever you need them for your answers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style="border: 1px solid black; display: flex; justify-content: center; width: 95%; text-align: center; padding: 1%;"&gt;à&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;ç&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;é&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;è&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;ê&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;ë&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;œ&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;î&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; ô&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;û&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;ù&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Modèle : YOU HEAR: Étienne, &lt;strong&gt;lorsque tu auras&lt;/strong&gt; du temps, téléphone-moi !&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;YOU WRITE: lorsque tu auras&lt;/p&gt;
